Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:29.25,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,That day, humanity remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.11,0:00:38.18,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,the terror of being ruled by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:45.24,Default,Narr,0,0,0,,The humiliation of being kept in a cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.41,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Prepare for combat!  ☮[Phr0stYsuBs]☮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:07.46,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,We have one target...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.93,0:01:11.89,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Defeat it, and make this humanity's\Nfirst base outside the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:14.30,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Target approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.58,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Split into five groups,\Njust as we practiced!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.56,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,We'll be the decoys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.35,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Attack teams, switch to\NThree-Dimensional Maneuver Gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.59,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,We'll strike from all directions at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:59.64,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,We'll show you the power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:00.93,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:39.99,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,To You, 2,000 Years in the Future\NThe Fall of Zhiganshina (1)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:09.15,Default,E,0,0,0,,Huh? Mikasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.43,Default,M,0,0,0,,Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.85,Default,E,0,0,0,,What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.80,Default,M,0,0,0,,You're so out of it.\NWere you sound asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.00,Default,E,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:24.70,Default,E,0,0,0,,It's just, I feel like I\Nhad a really long dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.39,Default,E,0,0,0,,What was it about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.38,Default,E,0,0,0,,I can't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.67,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren, why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.59,Default,M,0,0,0,,The Year: 845 Ã¢Â€Â” Zhiganshina District
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.00,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:52.35,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,These walls were constructed\Nwith God's wisdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:55.56,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,They were given to us by God himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.09,Default,Priest,0,0,0,,None may defile them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:07.32,Default,E,0,0,0,,Don't tell anyone that I was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.57,Default,M,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:12.58,Default,M,0,0,0,,But if you're crying for no reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,why not have your dad check you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:16.54,Default,E,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:18.83,Default,E,0,0,0,,I can't tell my dad about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:20.96,Default,H,0,0,0,,What are you crying over, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.15,Default,E,0,0,0,,Hannes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.72,Default,H,0,0,0,,Did Mikasa get mad at you for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.17,Default,E,0,0,0,,Why would that make me cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.58,Default,E,0,0,0,,And you stink of alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.28,Default,Soldiers,0,0,0,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.24,Default,E,0,0,0,,You're all drinking again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.23,Default,H,0,0,0,,Why don't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.92,Default,E,0,0,0,,Um, but don't you have work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.98,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yeah! We're guarding the gate today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:49.58,Default,H,0,0,0,,We spend all day here, so eventually,\Nwe get hungry and thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:53.34,Default,H,0,0,0,,And the fact that some of what\Nwe drink may be alcohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.37,Default,H,0,0,0,,Well, that isn't too big a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:59.21,Default,E,0,0,0,,Can you fight like that if you have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:02.35,Default,H,0,0,0,,If we have to? When would we...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:03.30,Default,E,0,0,0,,When else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.76,Default,E,0,0,0,,If they breached the walls\Nand entered the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.83,0:06:12.03,Default,H,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:15.42,Default,H,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren, don't yell like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:19.02,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,The doctor's son is pretty lively today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:23.63,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,If they ever do breach\Nthe walls, we'll do our jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:28.08,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,But that hasn't happened\Nfor a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.08,0:06:32.05,Default,E,0,0,0,,But my dad says that\Nyou're in the most danger
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,when you lower your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.93,Default,H,0,0,0,,Doctor Jaeger, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.04,Default,H,0,0,0,,Well, he's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:41.73,Default,H,0,0,0,,He once saved the whole\Ncity from an epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:44.65,Default,H,0,0,0,,We owe him more than we could ever repay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.94,0:06:47.92,Default,H,0,0,0,,But that has nothing to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.08,Default,H,0,0,0,,As a soldier, when you go\Nup to repair the walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you can sometimes see them,\Nwandering around outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:07:00.64,Default,H,0,0,0,,But this wall is fifty meters high.\NThey can't do anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.27,Default,E,0,0,0,,Th-Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:05.90,Default,E,0,0,0,,you're actually not prepared to fight them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.18,Default,H,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:09.54,Default,E,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:13.88,Default,E,0,0,0,,Then stop calling yourselves the Garrison,\Nand become the Wall Repair Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.70,Default,H,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:18.87,Default,H,0,0,0,,But listen, Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:22.71,Default,H,0,0,0,,If we're fighting,\Nit means things are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:27.80,Default,H,0,0,0,,As long as everyone's laughing at us\Nand calling us useless freeloaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that means we're all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.83,0:07:36.40,Default,E,0,0,0,,Even if we can never leave\Nthese walls for our entire lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:39.64,Default,E,0,0,0,,as long as we eat and\Nsleep, we'll survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.57,Default,E,0,0,0,,But that makes us just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like cattle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.75,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,That's a brave kid you have there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:54.92,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Not like he could do anything\Nabout it, huh, Hannes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:56.85,Default,H,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:00.47,Default,H,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:03.54,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Strange kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:08.59,Default,E,0,0,0,,Does he want to join the Survey Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:20.87,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren, you should stop\Nconsidering the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.25,Default,E,0,0,0,,What? You're going to tell\Nme they're stupid, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:28.16,Default,M,0,0,0,,That isn't it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.24,Default,E,0,0,0,,The Survey Corps is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.20,Default,E,0,0,0,,The front gate's opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.25,Default,E,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.63,Default,E,0,0,0,,The heroes are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.64,Default,E,0,0,0,,Damn it, I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.69,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,These are all that made it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:30.09,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,Everyone else must've been eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:34.20,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,That's what happens when\Nyou go outside the walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:37.09,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Moses! Moses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:41.44,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Um, my son, Moses... I don't see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.47,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.71,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,This is Moses's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:48.29,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.18,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,That is all we managed to retrieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:36.02,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,But my son...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:37.90,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,He helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:43.25,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Even if he didn't do anything directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.04,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,My son's death helped humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.38,0:10:48.54,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,fight back, didn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.16,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.12,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:05.52,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Our recon this time didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.68,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.33,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,we never...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.67,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,Never learn a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.69,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My own incompetence killed our men!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:27.64,Default,Soldier,0,0,0,,And we still don't even know what they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.23,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,What a mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.55,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,You've got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:41.35,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,It's like our taxes all\Ngo to fatten them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:46.54,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,What are you doing, stupid brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.44,Default,E,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Mikasa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:53.98,Default,Villager,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.36,Default,E,0,0,0,,Mikasa, you can let go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.23,Default,E,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:07.10,Default,E,0,0,0,,The firewood spilled everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.37,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:13.21,Default,M,0,0,0,,do you still want to join the Survey Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.78,Default,E,0,0,0,,Help me pick these up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:26.87,Default,M,0,0,0,,There isn't enough to bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:32.98,Default,M,0,0,0,,Information We Can Share So Far:\N\NAbout the Walls (1)\NHumanity lives within three walls.\NThe outermost is Wall Maria.\NThe second, Wall Rose.\NThe innermost is Wall Sina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:40.82,Default,M,0,0,0,,Information We Can Share So Far:\N\NAbout the Walls (2)\NDistance between each is roughly the same.\N100km separate Maria and Rose.\N130km separate Rose and Sina.\NFrom Sina to the center is about 250km.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:43.45,Default,M,0,0,0,,Back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.60,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.16,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Oh, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:53.50,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You actually worked hard for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.21,Default,E,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.87,Default,E,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.53,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Your ears turned red.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:03.34,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,That means you're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.59,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Mikasa helped you, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:09.32,Default,E,0,0,0,,Huh? Are you going somewhere, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.96,0:13:10.96,Default,E,0,0,0,,Work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:13.58,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm going inland to see patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.29,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Probably for two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.63,0:13:21.61,Default,M,0,0,0,,Eren said he wants to\Njoin the Survey Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.32,Default,E,0,0,0,,M-Mikasa, I told you not to tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:28.99,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:31.37,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:35.31,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Do you know how many people\Nhave died outside the walls?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:36.96,Default,E,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.00,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:38.90,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:43.38,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Why do you want to go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:48.76,Default,E,0,0,0,,I want to know what it's like out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:53.13,Default,E,0,0,0,,I don't want to spend my life inside\Nthe walls, not knowing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.77,Default,E,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If no one carries on their work,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.40,Default,E,0,0,0,,all the casualties till now\Nwill have been in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:06.86,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:10.14,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,The ship is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.58,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.05,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:14.45,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You need to talk to Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:18.02,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Karla, human curiosity is not something
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you can restrain with a lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:22.34,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.17,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,When I get back,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.84,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll show you what I've kept secret\Nin the basement all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:31.26,Default,E,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:36.81,Default,E,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.29,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.60,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Joining the Survey Corps?\NDon't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:45.65,Default,E,0,0,0,,Huh? Stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.76,Default,E,0,0,0,,I think people who're fine being cattle
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are way more stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:51.85,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.12,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Mikasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.82,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,sometimes he doesn't think things through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.71,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,When you're in trouble,\Nyou must help one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:03.19,Default,M,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.33,0:15:07.88,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,What's wrong, heretic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:11.85,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, hit back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:14.81,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:17.11,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,That would put me on your level!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.10,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:21.39,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,You know what I said is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:24.27,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,That's why you're hitting\Nme instead of arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:28.42,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean you admit I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:32.08,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Shut your damned mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:33.56,Default,E,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.24,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,That's Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:38.76,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,The fool's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.09,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,He wants to get his ass kicked?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:41.43,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,Let's give him what he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:44.59,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,M-Mikasa's here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:48.01,Default,Kids,0,0,0,,N-No... Let's get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.24,Default,E,0,0,0,,They ran away when they saw me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.95,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,No, they ran when they saw Mikasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:15:59.86,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.44,Default,E,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:08.36,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I can stand on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:10.32,Default,E,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:18.36,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,So I said that humanity should\Ngo out into the world someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.65,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,And they hit me and called me a heretic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.65,0:16:21.71,Default,E,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:27.64,Default,E,0,0,0,,Why does everyone act like you're\Ncrazy if you want to go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:32.79,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,Because staying within the walls has\Nbrought peace for a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:38.10,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,They're afraid that if many of us\Nventure out, we'll risk letting them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.37,0:16:43.98,Default,Blonde,0,0,0,,So the royal government declared\Nany interest in the outside world taboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:47.73,Default,E,0,0,0,,That's our lives we're risking,\Nso it's our business!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:49.19,Default,M,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.43,Default,M,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:55.92,Default,E,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, why\Ndid you tell my parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.58,Default,M,0,0,0,,I don't remember ever saying I'd help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:16:59.91,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,H-How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.58,Default,E,0,0,0,,Well... They weren't happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.42,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:11.67,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,But you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.39,0:17:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about those who think staying\Ninside the walls will protect us forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:18.98,Default,Kid,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.33,0:17:24.52,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Just because the walls haven't\Nbeen breached in a hundred years
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean they won't be
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,breached today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:51.59,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.64,Default,E,0,0,0,,An explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:54.67,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.13,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,I think something fell from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.07,Default,E,0,0,0,,Hey, Armin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.18,Default,E,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.65,0:18:07.52,Default,E,0,0,0,,What can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:19.11,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.62,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,That wall
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is fifty meters tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:25.95,Default,E,0,0,0,,It's one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.25,Default,E,0,0,0,,A Titan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:20.89,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,It broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.83,0:19:23.89,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,a hole in the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.89,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,They're coming inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.65,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,The Titans are getting inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:37.42,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,We have to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:38.90,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.65,Default,E,0,0,0,,My house is over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:42.41,Default,E,0,0,0,,My mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:44.66,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.54,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,It's all over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.75,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,The Titans are going
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to take the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:07.00,Default,E,0,0,0,,Nothing hit my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.81,Default,E,0,0,0,,Once I turn that corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:10.73,Default,E,0,0,0,,my house will still be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:16.45,Default,E,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.07,Default,E,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:22.84,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Eren...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.74,Default,E,0,0,0,,Mikasa, grab that side!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:26.09,Default,E,0,0,0,,We have to get this off her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:46.43,Default,E,0,0,0,,Hurry, Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.35,Default,M,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.79,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,The Titans are inside, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:53.85,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Eren, take Mikasa and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.07,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:56.86,Default,E,0,0,0,,I want to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.86,0:20:58.97,Default,E,0,0,0,,So hurry and get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:02.82,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,My legs were crushed by the rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.71,0:21:05.98,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Even if I get out, I can't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.34,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.32,Default,E,0,0,0,,Then I'll carry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:12.66,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Why do you never listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.82,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,At least listen this one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.50,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:19.81,Default,M,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.12,Default,M,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.05,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,If you don't go, all three of us will...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.06,0:21:26.90,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Hannes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:31.52,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Take the children and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:35.08,Default,H,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me, Karla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:39.37,Default,H,0,0,0,,I'll defeat the Titan, and save you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:41.01,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:42.44,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Don't try to fight it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:44.29,Default,H,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.29,0:21:46.11,Default,H,0,0,0,,If it were just the kids,\NI could save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:50.07,Default,H,0,0,0,,But I'm going to repay that family\Nfor what they've done for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:08.41,Default,E,0,0,0,,Wait, Hannes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.41,0:22:10.26,Default,E,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:12.77,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.52,Default,E,0,0,0,,My mom is still back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:18.44,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Eren! Mikasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:21.39,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,You must survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.17,0:22:35.79,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:49.93,Default,E,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:27.00,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,That day, humanity remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:34.76,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,{\i1}the terror of being ruled by them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:41.80,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,{\i1}The humiliation of being kept in a cage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:55.67,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,The Fall of Zhiganshina.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.33,0:24:00.83,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,All humanity could do\Nwas pray, scream, and die...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.71,0:24:03.33,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,Among them, Eren was
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.33,0:24:06.55,Default,Ar,0,0,0,,the only one to swear revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That Day\NThe Fall of Zhiganshina (2)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Illustration: Shuuzou Oshimi\N({\i1}The Flowers of Evil{\i0})
